Description: Variational Bayes Latent Patient Phenotyping using a variational Bayes Gaussian Mixture Model (VB-GMM) for Latent Class Analysis and variational Bayes regression for Biomarker level shifts, both implemented by Coordinate Ascent Variational Inference (CAVI) algorithms.
